description:
Data loaded from the PanCancer Atlas initiative on the GDC in Aug 2016. Contains batch effects normalized miRNA data.  

Note: This table was extracted from isb-cgc:pancancer_atlas.pancanMiRs_EBadjOnProtocolPlatformWithoutRepsWithUnCorrectMiRs_08_04_16. Data was annotated with ParticipantBarcode, SampleBarcode, AliquotBarcode, SampleTypeLetterCode, SampleType and TCGA Study.  

More details: https://gdc.cancer.gov/about-data/publications/pancanatlas BigQuery table: isb-cgc:pancancer_atlas.pancanMiRs_EBadjOnProtocolPlatformWithoutRepsWithUnCorrectMiRs_08_04_16

fields.description: TCGA barcode identifier for the study participant, eg TCGA-02-0001
fields.name: ParticipantBarcode

fields.description: Barcode of the biospecimen sample, eg TCGA-13-1489-02A
fields.name: SampleBarcode

fields.description: Letter code of the sample type using the TCGA standards, eg TPN, EBV. Full list available at https://gdc.cancer.gov/resources-tcga-users/tcga-code-tables/sample-type-codes
fields.name: SampleTypeLetterCode

fields.description: There are 10 sample types: Blood Derived Normal, Primary solid Tumor, Solid Tissue Normal, Recurrent Solid Tumor, Metastatic, Additional - New Primary, Primary Blood Derived Cancer - Peripheral Blood, Buccal Cell Normal, Additioanal Metastatic, Bone Marrrow Normal
fields.name: SampleType

fields.description: TCGA study abbreviation, eg LAML. Full list available at https://gdc.cancer.gov/resources-tcga-users/tcga-code-tables/tcga-study-abbreviations
fields.name: Study

fields.description: One of 1870 unique miRNA ids (aka symbols) contained in this table, eg hsa-mir-21 -- relevant reference information can be found in the isb-cgc:genome_reference dataset in the tables miRBase_v20 and miRBase_v20_hsa_gff3
fields.name: ID

fields.description: Normalized abundance (i.e., reads per million, RPM)
fields.name: miRNAexpr

fields.description: Corrected and Uncorrected indicator that specify if the miRs were corrected by the EBN+ method. See more details at https://www.synapse.org/#!Synapse:syn6171109
fields.name: Corrected
